{"tid":1874542,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情嚴重！子瑜中文喊話：大家好好戴口罩　粉絲搶購同款","createTime":"2020-02-11T09:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T11:53:42.000Z","uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"283ef021951e9fcbe59bc49e6d1ca4e3042eaf36","tid":1874542,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:09:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/1581408114-e446774a44d67f834b7deb1912848e6a-696x425.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F1581408114-e446774a44d67f834b7deb1912848e6a-696x425.jpg&h=a3acae5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜中文喊話戴口罩，粉絲想GET同款。（圖／VLIVE、Newsen YouTube） <br />\n<br />\n因新型冠狀病毒疫情（武漢肺炎）嚴重，不少韓星紛紛取消海內外演出，韓團TWICE雖然月初取消東京簽名會，但今（11日）、明在福岡的演唱會如期舉行，成員昨出境時口罩不離身，今演出前，子瑜開直播分享造型之外，也呼籲粉絲注意身體健康，以中文喊話：「大家要好好戴口罩！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/1581408104-e8373c661489a4a76ff4b7c1a8aa69f5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F1581408104-e8373c661489a4a76ff4b7c1a8aa69f5.png&h=036f0e88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE現身機場口罩不離身。（圖／Newsen YouTube）<br />\n<br />\nTWICE昨於仁川機場搭機飛往福岡，成員與工作人員，以及送、接機粉絲全數戴口罩，對於疫情不敢馬虎，粉絲也幽默表示，終於有錢能買跟偶像的「同款口罩」。她們連兩天在福岡國際會議場舉辦「TWICELIGHTS」演唱會，今晚出演前，子瑜率領成員開直播問候粉絲，要大家注意健康。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/1581408120-cf0d3fe970c6837b19ef20c88be3ebfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F1581408120-cf0d3fe970c6837b19ef20c88be3ebfa.jpg&h=ca59c453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜直播要大家注意健康。（圖／VLIVE）<br />\n<br />\n子瑜連開2次直播，笑說本來要演唱會結束再開，但因為瀏海太美，所以想展示給粉絲看，未來有機會想挑戰短髮；有人留言提到這次的疫情，要她注意身體健康，子瑜也呼籲大家要多喝熱水，先用韓文叮嚀後，再以中文表示：「大家要好好戴口罩！」但因各國口罩掃貨狀況嚴重，粉絲也留言詢問口罩是否充足，相當擔心子瑜口罩不夠用。<br />\n<br />\n此外，子瑜於過年期間，曾在IG以中韓語發文，除了拜年，也向醫護人員喊話：「你們辛苦了！」十分貼心。"},{"pid":"22dff127484ca91e5187cf3ebf15f14bd01da51b","tid":1874542,"uid":165368,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:10:32.000Z","msg":"竟然唔信政府?"},{"pid":"20fa8c30ae38d92192df876db919421e4b14db60","tid":1874542,"uid":42509,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:11:27.000Z","msg":"直播個樣咁撚醜既"},{"pid":"1d2dce4bd85a24621cca2b71a4a1e38adfdb46e6","tid":1874542,"uid":284119,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:12:14.000Z","msg":"直播好似大媽臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8739aa22af9e65f6a7e3eb16be19b8e6c07184","tid":1874542,"uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:13:41.000Z","msg":"懷疑定延識吸人美貌<br />\n牙愚愈黎愈柒<br />\n定延愈黎愈正"},{"pid":"d5270ebe809ca3bad32e30e55abfac1d2e0840d5","tid":1874542,"uid":61084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d2dce4bd85a24621cca2b71a4a1e38adfdb46e6","tid":1874542,"uid":284119,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:12:14.000Z","msg":"直播好似大媽臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:19:39.000Z","msg":"係囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚇鬼死心諗咩料"},{"pid":"b8c8ceaa675de8a96c922632632fc9a5813c5457","tid":1874542,"uid":231908,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:23:05.000Z","msg":"點解咁後生就走晒樣<br />\n<br />\n肯肯畀JYP上得多"},{"pid":"f62a098ea3c61bf4867bb8de9b5a917e3f52b677","tid":1874542,"uid":106348,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"20fa8c30ae38d92192df876db919421e4b14db60","tid":1874542,"uid":42509,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:11:27.000Z","msg":"直播個樣咁撚醜既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:24:29.000Z","msg":"人民幣 因為加咗人民幣"},{"pid":"7eab632147a1ff1763e8ecd1cdff3535d0fa59bb","tid":1874542,"uid":3405,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:33:35.000Z","msg":"支